genresAdvancedInfo.name: lancashire indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Lancashire indie is a subgenre of indie rock that originated in the Lancashire region of England. It is characterized by its raw, unpolished sound, often featuring distorted guitars and introspective lyrics. Lancashire indie bands often draw inspiration from the region's industrial past and working-class culture.
